      <Release_Notes>New Features &amp; Additions:
Added: Deep Neural Network (DNN)
Added: OpenVINO and CUDA backends on x64.

Structural &amp; Dependency Changes:
Moved external library dependencies to a separate package to allow updating the wrapper without having to update the dependencies every time</Release_Notes>
